{"tid":2146265,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"紐約州長稱新學年學生可恢復回校上課","createTime":"2020-08-08T12:55:06.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-08T12:55:06.000Z","uid":166360,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"d429502ddab79d553ef190a1bb9d14b343b1717f","tid":2146265,"uid":166360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T12:55:06.000Z","msg":"紐約州長稱新學年學生可恢復回校上課<br />\n2020-08-08 HKT 13:23<br />\n<br />\n&quot;美國紐約州長葛謨表示，由於州內的新型肺炎疫情轉趨平穩，在新學年學生可以恢復回校上課。&quot;<br />\n<br />\n&quot;過去兩個月，紐約市等州內多數地區，新型冠狀病毒檢測呈陽性反應的平均比率維持在1%左右。葛謨表示......只要學校所在區域的陽性反應平均比率低於5%，便可以選擇恢復面授上課、繼續網上授課，或者混合兩種形式......&quot;<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1542557-20200808.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1542557-20200808.htm&d=Ieu1u4uPL9fG%2BDPeYXLiW8rrJHX4TENqAnNRziDaZDA%3D&h=fa56f6c8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1542557-20200808.htm&h=fe2a1fd1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1542557-20200808.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"x-large\"><strong><span class=\"red\">香港檢測呈陽性反應的比率:  4,008/692,430 = 0.58%</span></strong></span>"}]}